name: Teejayx6
description: '''Dallas Antoino Asberry''' (born August 28, 2001),{{efn|Different sources list his name as Teejay Witherspoon,<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pitchfork.com/thepitch/teejayx6-interview/ |title=Teejayx6 Will Teach You How to Scam |date=2019-08-29 |access-date=2023-08-09 |website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]] |last=Pierre |first=Alphonse}}</ref> Dallas Witherspoon, or Dallas Antoino Karine Asberry<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.michiganresidentdatabase.com/person/159492072/dallas-asberry |title=Dallas Antoino-Karine Asberry, 17520 Monica St, Detroit, 48221 MI |access-date=2023-08-12 |website=Michigan Residents}}</ref>}} better known by his stage name '''Teejayx6''', is an American rapper. After emerging in the [[Detroit]] hip hop scene, he gained recognition for his subject matter of [[confidence trick|scamming]], [[identity theft]] and [[credit card fraud]] with his 2019 song "Dark Web". He is called the originator of this subgenre, which he refers to as "[[scam rap]]."
